---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import ureshino1 from "~/assets/hero_top1.png";
import logo from "~/assets/logomark.png";
import description from "~/assets/upgrade_your_life.png";
---

<div class="box">
  <div class="my-journey">
    <div class="overlap-group">
      <div class="title">
        <div class="header-mark"></div>
        <div class="text-wrapper">My Journey</div>
      </div>
      <img class="pearl" src="img/pearl1-3.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="overlap">
      <div class="div">
        <img class="flowers" src="img/flowers.svg" />
        <div class="scroll">
          <div class="scroll-2">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">電話占いに散財し恋愛に迷走</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/keyboard-double-arrow-down.svg" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="rectangle" src="img/rectangle-9.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">理想の王子様が見つかる</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">異業種交流会に参加</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/image.png" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="img" src="img/rectangle-9-2.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">ヨーロッパ社交界に参加</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">美容に無頓着</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/keyboard-double-arrow-down.png" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="img" src="img/rectangle-9-4.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">美容情報の発信者に</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">ぽっちゃり体型</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/keyboard-double-arrow-down-2.png" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="rectangle" src="img/rectangle-9-6.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">女性からも憧れの的</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">東京で会社経営</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/keyboard-double-arrow-down-4.png" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="img" src="img/rectangle-9-3.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">マレーシアに移住し新規ビジネス展開</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="frame"><div class="text-wrapper-2">SNS未活用</div></div>
              <img class="keyboard-double" src="img/keyboard-double-arrow-down-3.png" />
              <div class="frame-2">
                <img class="img" src="img/rectangle-9-5.png" />
                <div class="text-wrapper-3">大手出版社から写真集出版</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dots">
          <div class="ellipse"></div>
          <div class="ellipse-2"></div>
          <div class="ellipse-3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img class="pearl-2" src="img/pearl2-4.png" />
    </div>
    <img class="pearl-3" src="img/pearl2-5.png" />
  </div>
</div>

